snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator | Wallace & Gromit Special Pack Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Hold onto your teapots, Washers! It's time for another cracking adventure!

We'll be taking a trip down to 62 West Wallaby Street in our Wallace & Gromit Special Pack. 

Coming to PowerWash Simulator on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch, Xbox Series S|X, Xbox One, Windows, and Steam in 2025.

Wishlist on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3077590

Play PowerWash Simulator on Steam here: https://steamcommunity.com/app/1290000
